RE: How do I deal with shame and guilt? (29-07-2012 10:16 AM)MNeufs Wrote: Hey guys, so lately I've been dealing with some shame and guilt for the last few hours in my life. Is there any way you guys can help me? It's hard to say stuff nowadays without someone getting mad. Can you help?
Apologize if it doesn't hurt you or them, and forgive your self.
Realize that guilt is a tool that lets you know you do not have to reply the past.
