RE: How do I deal with shame and guilt? Take it easy then. If you're like me you're probably worried a. she wants to make fun of me b. does she like me at all? If you're again like me, you'll overthink this and stuff it up. If however you can show her that you're not bothered by it somehow... this is where it's a gray area because I'm always bothered by stuff like that so my advice is theoretical... but if you can just, next time you see her, make a joke about it and smile, show that you aren't gonna resent her for it, then you my friend might just get somewhere The following 2 users Like morondog's post:2 users Like morondog's post
